*******************************************************************************
       Name: Pale Imprint
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_CHAR_SELF
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 12
 Wait Beats: 12
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: The Pale Ledger's imprint fades from your awareness.
Acquisition:
   - Psionicist: level 10
Description:
   Pale Imprint is a Psionicist utility spell that creates a persistent
   mental snapshot of the current area's layout and inhabitants. By
   impressing the surroundings onto a psionic "ledger" in their mind, the
   Psionicist gains a detailed awareness of the room's magical properties
   and hidden features.

   The Pale Imprint allows the Psionicist to detect hidden objects and
   doors more easily, notice subtle magical disturbances, and maintain
   a mental map of nearby terrain. The imprint fades over time as new
   information overwrites it. In practice, it is used by Psionicists who
   need to navigate unfamiliar or trapped environments with greater safety
   than their unaided senses would provide.
*******************************************************************************
